race.description: Gold Coast Turf Club Magic Millions Country Cup
race.comment: The $500,000 Country Cup. REVOLT (6) resumes here but did string six wins together on the bounce when last in work and was racing with a lot of confidence. Has won four of five over this six-furlong journey and gets hoop Lane on top to navigate from the sticky alley. Can return in winning order. PARTY SPIRIT (9) has been right there in all four runs this campaign and will be cherry-ripe fit for this. Looms as the main danger. OBEROI PRINCESS (10) has a handy record over this distance range with three wins and three seconds from 12 attempts. In the mix on best figures. LETMELETGO (5) is improving with racing this time in and gets McDonald in the saddle. Shouldn't be underestimated. ASTRA STAR (17) goes well for rider Cormack who has two wins and four placings from just eight steers. Include from the favourable draw.
